 &lt;strong>TL;DR&lt;/strong>: Create &lt;code>.config/cem.yaml&lt;/code> to configure file patterns, output paths, and dev server options. Most users only need &lt;code>generate.files&lt;/code> and &lt;code>generate.output&lt;/code>. See the 
&lt;a href="#configuration-file">complete example
&lt;/a> below for all options.
