&lt;p>You can configure &lt;code>cem&lt;/code> via a &lt;code>cem.yaml&lt;/code> file in your project&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code>.config&lt;/code> directory, or by using command-line flags.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>